title: Growing Neurons to Heal Brain Damage

media:group.media:title: Growing Neurons to Heal Brain Damage
media:group.media:description: Watch as primordial  neural cells dance across, grow into, and even move 3D scaffolds engineered to heal brain injury from stroke and other trauma. Decorating the scaffold with various nutrients and biochemical signals allow researchers to control what types of brain tissues they become. Learn more at https://pratt.duke.edu/about/news/npc-growth-scaffold
